1. THE GRANT
Citrus Interactive ("the Licensor") hereby grants you a non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free license to view, download, and modify the source code and assets of Splashout for the sole purpose of creating "Mods" (modifications, extensions, or derivative content that requires the original game to function).

2. PERMITTED USE 
Creation: You may create, test, and run Mods for personal use.
Distribution of Mods: You may distribute your Mod (the modified files/code you created) to other users, provided that your Mod does not contain the original game’s executable or substantial core assets.
Non-Commercial: Mods must be distributed free of charge. You may not sell Mods or lock them behind a permanent paywall, though voluntary "tips" (e.g., Ko-fi or Patreon) are permitted.

3. RESTRICTIONS
No Game Redistribution: You may not redistribute the full Splashout game, its compiled binaries, or its core proprietary assets as a standalone product.
No Commercial Exploitation: You may not use the source code or assets to create a competing commercial product or a "fork" sold under a different name.
Attribution: Any distributed Mod must include a notice stating: "This mod was created for Splashout by Citrus Interactive. Original game remains the property of Citrus Interactive."

4. CONTRIBUTIONS
By submitting a "Pull Request" or contribution directly to the official Splashout repository, you grant Citrus Interactive a perpetual, irrevocable license to use, modify, and include your contribution in the official version of the game.

5. TERMINATION
This license terminates automatically if you fail to comply with any of its terms. Citrus Interactive reserves the right to revoke modding privileges for specific individuals who violate community standards or intellectual property rights.
